sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Client
    participant API as API Server<br/>(ml-pipeline)<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL / PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant ObjStore as MinIO / S3 / GCS<br/>9000/443 TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow
    participant Driver as Driver Container
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Launcher as Launcher Container
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWF as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Controller

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,ObjStore: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution
        User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP<br/>Auth: SubjectAccessReview
        API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>SQL 3306/5432 TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
        API->>ObjStore: Store pipeline spec<br/>S3 API 9000/TCP<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
        API->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        K8s-->>Argo: Workflow created
        Argo->>Driver: Execute driver container<br/>(in-pod)
        Driver->>MLMD: Create MLMD execution<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP<br/>Auth: None
        Driver->>API: Cache key lookup<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Argo->>Launcher: Execute launcher container<br/>(in-pod)
        Launcher->>ObjStore: Download inputs / Upload outputs<br/>S3 API 9000/TCP<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
        Launcher->>MLMD: Publish execution metadata<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP<br/>Auth: None
        PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow status<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        PA->>API: ReportWorkflow<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP<br/>Auth: Projected SA token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over User,SWF: Flow 2: Scheduled Pipeline Execution
        User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringruns<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP<br/>Auth: SubjectAccessReview
        API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        SWF->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        SWF->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow (v1)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount
        SWF->>API: CreateRun (v2 pipelines)<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP<br/>Auth: Projected SA token
    end
